Remove All FID Assignments

Are you sure you want to remove ALL FID assignments?

This action cannot be undone. All FCC IDs will become unassigned.

Reassign All FIDs

This will clear all existing assignments and auto-assign fresh FID numbers to all FCC IDs.

FIDs will be assigned in order: Non-chip/Chip keys first, then Remote Head/Flip keys, then Proximity keys.
